________________________________________________________________________

Just a basic no-thrills site-generator
It will take "MD-flavored" files and make them in to simple HTML

See https://github.com/imlinus/personal for an example in action


Install
________________________________________________________________________

mkdir modules
cd modules
git submodule add https://github.com/imlinus/site-generator.git



site-generator.config.js
________________________________________________________________________

import SiteGenerator from './modules/site-generator/source/index.js'

new SiteGenerator({
  root: '',
  pages: 'pages',
  posts: 'posts',
  build: 'build',
  feed: {}
})


Basic structure
________________________________________________________________________

/templates
  page.html
  post.html
/pages
  index
  about
/posts
  2021-12-31-example


